nodes.text: Galagolos V, also known more simply as Galagalos was a swampy and stinky planet located in the galaxy's Colonies region that was the homeworld of the Cloddogran Bargwill Tomder. The pirate Hondo Ohnaka once crash-landed a ship in a spaceport on Galagolos V during the reign of the Galactic Empire.
